A file `"students.txt"` contains the following two lines:

```
Alice 90
Bob 75
```

Determine the output of the following code (the method declares `throws IOException`):

```java
Scanner sc = new Scanner(new File("students.txt"));
ArrayList<String> names = new ArrayList<String>();
int total = 0;
while (sc.hasNext())
{
    String name = sc.next();
    int score = sc.nextInt();
    names.add(name);
    total += score;
}
sc.close();
System.out.println(names.get(0) + " " + total);
```

Determine the output of the following code:

```java
String data = "12 blue\n18 green\ncat 5";
Scanner scan = new Scanner(data);
int count = 0;
int sum = 0;

while (scan.hasNext())
{
    if (scan.hasNextInt())
    {
        sum += scan.nextInt();
        count++;
    }
    else
    {
        scan.next();
    }
}
scan.close();
System.out.print(count + " " + sum);
```

